title: Theresa Barnwell showed up in New York City after Clinton's 11/11 medical accident?
subtitle: :: Hillaires Budible took over Twitter with allegations that Teresa Barnwell appeared in New York to impersonate Hillary Clinton after she left the candidate in 9/11 following a medical accident.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: The woman who appeared in New York after Hillary Clinton left a memorial ceremony on 9/11 for medical reasons was the double body of Teresa Barnwell, not Clinton herself.
